                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The vampire spawn deals [[/r 1d6 #precision]]{1d6 extra precision damage} to flat-footed creatures.<br />When the monster Strikes a creature that has the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} condition with an agile or finesse melee weapon, an agile or finesse unarmed attack, or a ranged weapon attack, it also deals the listed precision damage. For a ranged attack with a thrown weapon, that weapon must also be an agile or finesse weapon.</p>"
